            <title>[LU-11920] memory leak in lod_lds_buf_get()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11920</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lod_lds_buf_get() introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11739&quot; title=&quot;Don&amp;#39;t inherit default layout from root for new subdirectories&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11739&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11739&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; can cause memory leak as it resets lds_def_comp_entries unconditionally while it can contain a valid pointer to buffer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
